Detailed Description

Structure to encapsulate AT response parameters. Response parameters can be either numeric or strings NOTE: It is not allowed to derive from AtResponseParameter (no virtual destructor).

Member Enumeration Documentation

enum AtResponseParameter::ParamType
 

Type for parameters - either string, numeric or novalue.

Enumerator:
PtNumeric  For all numeric parameters that fit into the range of INT32.
PtString  For all other parameters that have a value.
PtNoValue  Only allowed if the parameter.
